":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"974c7067-7267-4717-813d-397586cf7412","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"んー。mac ユーザじゃないので分からないす。","ts":"1530940443.000024","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"dd8cd0a9-8b73-4087-bd04-02e4e3a8cd3a","type":"message","user":"U72TB62UF","text":"日本語入力を親指シフトにしていて、短い時間で一気にアルファベットを出力（ohayou）→日本語にする（おはよう）という形にすると発声しやすいようです。\nローマ字入力だと発生しないため、上記のような特殊なケースで発生するぽいですねえ。","ts":"1530940505.000029","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"fd193472-c35d-4efe-a385-8a73217967b3","type":"message","user":"U72TB62UF","text":"Windowsだと発生しないため、謎感あります。","ts":"1530940522.000069","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"dd22c044-4fcd-4566-ab32-0f208d5ec554","type":"message","user":"U03C4RC8X","text":"(もしかしてMMK事案かな)","ts":"1530940558.000052","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"2091d6f6-dcdb-4fb8-b2eb-aa5ad046041a","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"Multi Media Kiosk","ts":"1530940625.000080","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"fcc89daa-eb2d-4244-b6e3-8bd4072d858d","type":"message","user":"U72TB62UF","text":"Moji Moji Kunn","ts":"1530940839.000002","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"e243326f-9fe4-4d44-951d-7b3c56fa2264","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"`guifontwide` を設定しているせいかもなぁ。時間がある時に `guifontwide` の設定を消して `guifont` の設定だけでも同じことが起こるか試してみてください。\n\n例えば `:let &amp;guifont=&amp;guifontwide` `:set guifontwide&amp;` すると guifont にヒラギノが入るんでその状態でも同じことが起こるか。","ts":"1530941860.000013","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"372f2228-3793-4be6-8700-dfb54abc0624","type":"message","user":"U06BRP8VD","text":"あとはやっぱ1行500文字ってのはVimには長すぎるんですよね。使い方なのでとやかく言えるアレではないんですが、論理改行と物理改行分けて考えて、物理改行は長くとも200文字(できれば100文字)以内にしておくと、いろいろストレスなくなります。","ts":"1530941981.000045","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"6894ae4f-d4f8-46b5-af8d-b3c9f668748f","type":"message","user":"U72TB62UF","text":"上記設定を試しましたが、同様の入力の表示遅延と表示ズレが発生しました。","ts":"1530943159.000031","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"9b017f26-5683-471a-bce2-9e5d2616a6fd","type":"message","user":"U72TB62UF","text":"synmaxcolが有るように、そもそもの使いかたではないのは承知しています。\nJpFormatプラグインとかを駆使しなくてもいい方法はないかなぁと探しているところでした。","ts":"1530943278.000072","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"15b0c410-e623-4bd5-ae72-e5b47a0567b4","type":"message","user":"U72TB62UF","text":"<https://sites.google.com/site/fudist/Home/jpformat>","ts":"1530943280.000050","attachments":[{"fallback":"JpFormat.vim - Vim日本語整形プラグイン - fudist","id":1,"title":"JpFormat.vim - Vim日本語整形プラグイン - fudist","title_link":"https://sites.google.com/site/fudist/Home/jpformat","image_url":"https://sites.google.com/site/fudist/_/rsrc/1258592004984/Home/jpformat/JpFormat.jpg?height=150&width=200","blocks":null,"service_name":"sites.google.com","service_icon":"https://ssl.gstatic.com/sites/p/2bf40e/system/app/images/apple-touch-icon.png","from_url":"https://sites.google.com/site/fudist/Home/jpformat","original_url":"https://sites.google.com/site/fudist/Home/jpformat"}],"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"d50e8eec-d31d-4142-9fa1-fb37dc461045","type":"message","user":"U72TB62UF","text":"Windowsのメモ帳でも問題にならないようなところがvimだと難しいというのはなんだか不思議。","ts":"1530943421.000016","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"09fc9770-1170-4501-97a2-caa00485d432","type":"message","user":"U03C6TEAZ","text":"Monospace じゃないのかも","ts":"1530943782.000054","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"8d7c0158-0644-4768-a861-832d58163556","type":"message","user":"U03C4RC8X","text":"Mata MacVim Ka","ts":"1530943974.000039","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"type":"message","user":"UBMHEQF55","text":"<@UBMHEQF55> has joined the channel","ts":"1530946111.000076","subtype":"channel_join","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null},{"client_msg_id":"59216339-23fc-4caf-b649-13a4aa2726d6","type":"message","user":"UBMHEQF55","text":"はじめまして, いきなりなんですが, 質問があります.\njで下に移動してから, kを押して, 上に移動しようとすると, 右に移動してしまいます.\nそのあと, kを押せば, 上に移動してくれます. \n\n逆に, kを押したあとに, jで下に移動しようとすると, 移動せず, もう一度jを押せば移動します.\n以前はこの症状がなかったように思えます.\n\nwindows pro 10で, WSLで, ubuntu18.04を動かしています.\n\npluginは, pathogenで、 NERDTreeを入れています.\n\n.vimrcファイルは下記のようになっています.\n```\n\" set leader \",\"\nlet mapleader = \",\"\n\n\" about tabs\nset tabstop=4 \"tabspot is the unmber of spaces a &lt;TAB&gt; counts for.\nset expandtab \" a tab turns into just \"four spaces\".\n\n\" UI config\nset number \" show line numbers\nset cursorline \" highlight the current line\nset showmatch \" highlight matching {}, [], ()\n\n\" searching setting\nset incsearch \" start searching as soon as you start typing\nset hlsearch \" highlight the matches\n\" \nnnoremap &lt;leader&gt;&lt;space&gt; :nohlsearch&lt;CR&gt; \n\n\" movement setting\n\"move vertically by visula line\nnnoremap j gj\nnnoremap k gk\n\n\" move to beginning/end of line\nnnoremap E $\nnnoremap B ^\n\n\" $/^ doesn't do anything\nnnoremap $ &lt;nop&gt;\nnnoremap ^ &lt;nop&gt;\n\n\" mapping jk to &lt;ESC&gt;\nnnoremap jk &lt;ESC&gt; \n\n\" pathogen setting\nexecute pathogen#infect()\nautocmd VimEnter * NERDTree\n```","ts":"1530946751.000040","edited":{"user":"UBMHEQF55","ts":"1530946825.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"e70979fc-5af7-4dcf-80d3-271840ff9b0a","type":"message","user":"UBMHEQF55","text":"どなたか原因がわかる方いらっしゃいませんか?","ts":"1530946845.000062","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"25973927-96c3-4970-b754-35eb4eab82a4","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"何か余計なマッピングがされている可能性が高いです。\n`:map j` `:map k` で確認してみると良さそうです","ts":"1530946893.000001","team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"f8dcc635-70eb-485e-a27a-9670f1bad547","type":"message","user":"UBMHEQF55","text":"`n  jk          * &lt;Esc&gt;&lt;Space&gt; ` `:map j` の結果\n`No mapping found ` `:map k` の結果","ts":"1530946931.000073","edited":{"user":"UBMHEQF55","ts":"1530946977.000000"},"team":"T03C4RC8V","replace_original":false,"delete_original":false,"blocks":null,"source_team":"T03C4RC8V","user_team":"T03C4RC8V"},{"client_msg_id":"33f711fe-fc4c-4935-86c2-74af893209af","type":"message","user":"U03C71D7H","text":"その jk のマッピングが原因ですね。よく見たら vimrc に普通に書いてあった","ts":"1530946994.000020","team":"T03C4R